(1,'en-Us','Monster card','Monster Cards represent monsters that players battle against each other or directly against either player during the Battle Phase. Monsters are the foundation of any Duel.','https://res.cloudinary.com/imgresd/image/upload/v1687284428/YGOWiki/MonsterCardEN_lr9plu.png')
