(2,'en-Us','Spell Card','Cards with green-colored borders that have various effects to alter the play of the game. Often, a Spell Card has a single effect to provide a bonus to the user or a weakness to the opponent. Unlike Trap Cards, Spell Cards have the advantage of being able to be played without having to be Set first.','https://res.cloudinary.com/imgresd/image/upload/v1687298873/YGOWiki/SpellCardEN_fua63a.png')
Insert Into [dbo].[TranslatedCardTypes] ([OriginalCardTypeId],[LanguageId],[TranslatedName],[TranslatedDescription],[ImageExample])
Values
(2,'es-Mx','Carta Mágica','Son de color verde y pueden tener varios efectos que alteran un Duelo. Suelen tener efectos que benefician al controlador de la carta, o perjudican al adversario. Aunque las Cartas Mágicas no suelen ser tan poderosas como las de Trampa, tienen la ventaja de que se pueden usar en el mismo turno sin tener que Colocarlas antes. ','https://res.cloudinary.com/imgresd/image/upload/v1687298874/YGOWiki/SpellCardES_imtzee.png')
