(3,'en-Us','Trap Card','Cards with purple-colored borders that have various effects. A Trap Card must first be Set and can only be activated after the current turn has finished. After that, it may be activated during either player''s turn.','https://res.cloudinary.com/imgresd/image/upload/v1687299218/YGOWiki/TrapCardEN_q3vhwt.png')
