(1,'en-Us','Gemini','They are treated as Normal Monsters on the field and in the GY, and can gain their effects by performing an additional Normal Summon on them while they are face-up on the field.','https://res.cloudinary.com/imgresd/image/upload/v1687461144/YGOWiki/GeminiEN_fgbuya.png')
