(4,'en-Us','Field Spell Card','Which have a compass rose symbol. , have the advantage of being able to change the entire state of play for its controller''s or for both players'' side of the field. They are Spell Speed 1 and are placed on the Field Zone, apart from the Spell & Trap Zones.','https://res.cloudinary.com/imgresd/image/upload/v1687674784/FieldSpellEN_re1f4d.png')
